 Regarding "World War II: When Lions Roared" (NBC, April 19-20): I was very 
disappointed in Part 2 of this movie.It was very shallow. No mention of Japan 
and Italy's part in the war. No mention of the atomic bomb dropped on Japan; no 
mention of Hirohito -- or Mussolini. No mention of the surrender to Gen. 
Douglas MacArthur on the battleship Missouri. No mention of Adm. Nimitz. In 
other words, very shallow. 
</P>
