<P>
 I enjoyed Suzanne Lummis' tribute to Charles Bukowski (April 10). Thank you 
for publishing it. I attended the March 26 event at Arundel. For another take 
on what happened that evening, please note the enclosed poem. 
</P>
<P>
 The Wake 
</P>
<P>
 Buk died and Andernach slept another day and the 
</P>
<P>
 wake was held at a bookstore 
</P>
<P>
 and maybe 3 poets and 30 typists and 300 secret poets 
</P>
<P>
 showed up 
</P>
<P>
 only two drunks showed up and one of 
</P>
<P>
