TO FILL EXECUTIVE POSITIONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Lorna Nahil has been appointed vice president, sales operations for Ingram 
Micro Inc., a Santa Ana wholesale distributor of microcomputer products.Nahil 
was previously general manager, commercial finance, and chief financial officer 
for the distribution services company of Douglas Aircraft, a division of 
McDonnell Douglas. In addition, Sam M. Atassi has joined the company as 
director of its Latin American export headquarters in Miami. He was formerly 
director of products and purchasing for Merisel's Latin American operation. 
Atassi was also an international sales manager with Comptronics Inc. in Miami 
and an international trading engineer with Sarouba Florida Inc. 
</P>
