<HEADLINE>
<P>
AN UNSIGHTLY STRETCH OF VENTURA BOULEVARD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I was surprised to find no mention in your story "Ventura Blvd. Faces a Long 
Road Back" (April 23) of the monstrosity on Ventura one block east of Woodman 
Avenue. 
</P>
<P>
 This whole block is an eyesore of graffiti, broken-down stores and homeless 
