<HEADLINE>
<P>
MISSING MENTION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Your "expert's" advice in "Travel Insider" ("Dollars Buy More Again in 
Europe," April 17), surprised me since he did not mention the benefits of using 
a credit card when traveling. In 95% of the instances that I have used a credit 
card in Europe, I have "made money" when the bills finally come in to be paid.  
</P>
<P>
 RICHARD J. WARREN 
</P>
<P>
 Van Nuys 
</P>
