<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 15, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Magazine; Part 2; Page 20; Column 1; Magazine Desk 
